{"tid":2089851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好用「黃就唔屌得」嘅心態來幫某指定傳媒開脫，所有出人大頭搞到手足出事嘅傳媒就係冇傳媒道德！","createTime":"2020-07-02T00:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T01:46:31.000Z","uid":231922,"like":10,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25172a0411fca7271e769548af8285151219e77a","tid":2089851,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T00:51:39.000Z","msg":"唔開名。<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，論冇道德，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有出人大頭搞到人地有人身危險嘅傳媒，都係冇道德，唔理嗰個傳媒本身偏向邊一邊。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n正如德國出報導，如果預料有機會令上鏡人士有人身危險，一定blur樣。<br />\n<br />\n某大台嗰啲或者其他紅媒我地都屌開，大家心照。<br />\n<br />\n唔好用黃就唔屌得呢啲借口開脫，唔啱就係唔啱。"},{"pid":"97181f340818a28216dd7fc52f676ba3de503433","tid":2089851,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T00:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88sx4kO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88sx4kO.gif&h=a13f5c98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f44857be65b71e4929eb636e27d8e52cfb03667a","tid":2089851,"uid":231922,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"97181f340818a28216dd7fc52f676ba3de503433","tid":2089851,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T00:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88sx4kO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88sx4kO.gif&h=a13f5c98&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"呢件事已經超越「唔完美」嘅底線，根本要屌。<br />\n當然，對住同路人，我地梗係想佢「改善」行先。"},{"pid":"159cb21a31514b65d610e952eb510ccf83811460","tid":2089851,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"屌立場班五毛唔去屌cctvb？cctvb仲早過立場，當時live晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e9c2aea773ce073d0d1f73b278878f71a084cd4d","tid":2089851,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-